- terminal 1: open simulation environment

$ ros2 launch turtlebot3_gazebo turtlebot3_school.launch.py

- terminal 2: turn on slam nodes(cartographer)

$ ros2 launch turtlebot3_cartographer cartographer.launch.py use_sim_time:=true

- terminal 3: turn on heuristic motor controller

$ ros2 run teleop_twist_keyboard teleop_twist_keyboard

- terminal 4: type this command and press enter when you want to save map

$ ros2 run nav2_map_server map_saver_cli -f ~/map
